        "reaction_type": "加氢裂化反应",
        "reaction_type_english": "Hydrocracking reaction",
        "description": "在连续微圆柱反应器中，使用不同方法制备的SiO2/Zr催化剂，在500°C、氢气氛围下，对粗棕榈油(CPO)进行催化加氢裂化，以生产生物燃料（生物航空燃料、生物柴油和生物汽油）。",
        "text_snippet": "The activity of the catalysts was explored in crude palm oil (CPO) hydrocracking, conducted under a continuous system micro-cylindrical reactor... The catalytic hydrocracking was carried out in a continuous system micro-cylindrical reactor... CPO feed is injected using a syringe pump into the reactor with a feed flow rate of 20 mL/h. 0.5 g of catalyst was employed, and the hydrocracking was conducted at 500 ◦C for 1 h with an H2 flow rate of 30 mL/h.",
        "reaction_type_classify": "Hydrogenation reaction"
      }
    ]
